[NPC] Darphen: I suppose you mean to convince me to let them off their debt.
[NPC] Darphen: That will not happen.
[NPC] Darphen: Their taxes must be paid if the family is to keep the home.
[NPC] Darphen: Do you have the 50,000 tria needed to save it?

